name: Cypherpunk Launches Zcash Treasury With $50M Backing
description: Clad in wet porcelain and brass, the mechanical saint enacts the high rite of zero-knowledge, sealing the pulsing lattice of the treasury. Beneath the tungsten glare and the algorithmic privacy veil, the self-sovereign capital is accumulated, ensuring the cold, hard logic of the secure data vault.
